CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Highest Performances Holdings Inc, formerly PUYI INC, is a China-based company primarily provides wealth management services. The Company provides a series of comprehensive financial asset allocation services including wealth management services, asset management services, insurance consulting services, trust consulting services and ancillary services. The Company's corporate finance service business primarily includes financing solutions for corporate borrowers. These programs include product design, funding source identification and compliance and risk management. The Company's asset management business mainly includes managing two funds (FoF) and preparing new FoF and non-performing loan (NPL) funds.
